New to Microsoft 365 in July—updates to Azure AD, Microsoft Teams, Outlook,
and more

   This month, we’re announcing updates to Azure AD, Microsoft Defender
   ATP, Teams, Outlook, Desktop Analytics, and Office 365 ProPlus to help
   you be more productive, improve your security posture, and streamline
   IT management.
